UID:2CdTsHr8hyP3GK0nRn8iG
SUMMARY:Kickstands Up! All Motorcycle Club Day
DTSTAMP:20260407T043747Z
DTSTART:20260425T100000Z
DESCRIPTION:Inviting all motorcycle clubs to roll on down to MOHAI! Indicat
	e your Motorcycle Cub membership and receive $5 off admission all day\\\, 
